01:03:21.999 --> 01:03:23.125
FORÇA-TAREFA DE DROGAS
SGT. CHOI KYUNGDO

01:03:57.459 --> 01:03:58.876
INSPETOR JANG

01:04:09.834 --> 01:04:13.792
NOVATO

